{title: Unclosed Tags}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]This has an <b>unclosed bold tag
[C]Does the bold continue here?
[D]Or does it stop at end of [G]line?
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[G]Unclosed <i>italic starts here
[C]What happens to this line?
[D]And this one [G]too?
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]<b>Bold that never closes
[G]Keeps on going
[D]Through the whole [G]chorus
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[G]Nested unclosed: <b>bold <i>and italic
[C]Both unclosed at the same [D]time
{end_of_verse}
